                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18410104-423-offence-1 t18410104-cd-16"></join>12th of De<lb></lb>cember</rs>, 1 pair of boots, value 38<hi rend="italic">s</hi>., the goods of <persName id="t18410104-name-137" type="victimName">
